## **Solution:**

This is the easiest challenge of the whole category. All you need to do is check the comments on the YouTube video to find the following comment:

![Comment of the flag](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*kiJaDKPXgaBiFahZTUW1hQ.png)

